{{Infobox book| |name =Son of Retro Pulp Tales |image =Sonofretropulptales.jpg |caption='''Artwork by [[Timothy Truman]]''' |author =[[Joe R. Lansdale]] |illustrator= |cover_artist=[[Tim Truman]] |country =United States |language =English |series = |genre =[[Horror fiction|Horror]], short story collection |publisher =[[Subterranean Press]] |pub_date =2009 |media_type =Print [[hardcover]], [[limited edition]] |pages =211 |isbn =978-1-59606-260-3 |preceded_by=Cross Plains Universe: Texans Celebrate Robert E. Howard (with Scott A. Cupp, (2006) |followed_by=Crucified Dreams (2011)}}
